---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy | Hotel Iubit" description="Learn more about Refund Policy at Hotel Iubit.">
  <div class="bg-dark text-white py-16 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold">Refund Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl prose prose-lg prose-primary">
      <p>Last updated: July 23, 2026</p>
      
      <h2>1. Standard Cancellation and Refunds</h2>
      <p>For standard room bookings, guests may cancel their reservation free of charge up to <strong>48 hours</strong> prior to the scheduled check-in time. Cancellations made within the 48-hour window will incur a cancellation fee equal to the first night's room rate and applicable taxes.</p>
      
      <h2>2. Non-Refundable Reservations</h2>
      <p>Certain promotional rates, advance purchase bookings, or special packages may be strictly non-refundable. For these reservations, no refunds or modifications will be permitted once the booking is confirmed, regardless of the cancellation timeframe.</p>
      
      <h2>3. No-Shows and Early Departures</h2>
      <p>In the event of a "no-show" (failing to arrive on the scheduled check-in date without prior notice), a penalty fee will be charged, typically equivalent to the first night's stay, and the remainder of the reservation will be cancelled without refund.</p>
      <p>If you choose to depart earlier than your scheduled checkout date, an early departure fee may apply, and refunds for any unused nights are subject to the hotel's discretion.</p>
      
      <h2>4. Extra Charges and Meals</h2>
      <p>Please note that all meal services at our hotel are separate and incur extra charges. Pre-paid meals or dining packages are subject to their own specific cancellation terms and may be non-refundable if cancelled on short notice.</p>
      
      <h2>5. Processing Refunds</h2>
      <p>Approved refunds will be processed back to the original method of payment used at the time of booking. Please allow <strong>5 to 10 business days</strong> for the refunded amount to reflect in your account, depending on your bank or credit card issuer.</p>
      
      <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you need to request a refund, modify a reservation, or have any questions about this policy, please contact our front desk team by phone, email, or in person.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
